Class LogModel

com.visionreport.core.models.LogModel
public final class LogModel extends Object
Internal data model representing a single log event (step) within a test case, used by the Vision Report rendering engine.

Mirrors the API-level Log but is designed specifically for internal processing and FreeMarker template binding. Contains only serializable, presentation-ready fields such as Status, formatted timestamps, and optional Base64-encoded media.

Usage: Created and populated internally by ReportGenerator. Not intended for direct use by end users.
